{"h1f538748g72e4g47a8g9f42ga6220d162c5b": ["I buried my daughter because of you. I'm going nowhere. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "f4419e1b-a770-0332-db30-5885eb252a42"], "h1fd7301eg8ec5g4127ga77ag9c40d45bd621": ["I've prayed many times over that Silvanus return me to that moment.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "bc5b4293-88eb-23f1-438a-a8a6b04f9f09"], "h2a6053acg8e76g44fcgabffgd36d0ce6db64": ["I am sorry, a hundred times over, and a hundred more yet.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "61b84200-a39e-e0a2-7ea5-7e3c6a5a2871"], "h6ad1c9aege0eag4de4g9208gc251d95d95f8": ["Tell me - how's the wine? ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "791ce990-e707-e3fe-b8b6-161954a45476"], "hb0b69f55g7f46g4935gbed7gcb7a16521777": ["The wine? What did you...", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "fb897176-ba46-1ebc-195b-d14e43e9e728"], "hcf31fd56gebb7g459agbdb3ga16e7beb3492": ["I want you to feel small. I want you to feel helpless. Just like her. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "39755ca4-44ec-0683-8b20-39a191e989e3"], "ha38aa706gbb8eg479cgb232g00cd8579a1c5": ["Her name was Arabella. Picture her. How scared she was. And know - this will <i>hurt</i>. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "5c85a9e4-ba15-930d-9d53-b5fc6fe0c6ea"], "h11ee989cg9ecag4e94gbbdbgce9b2b1843cc": ["If you do this you are no better than her. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "77268077-32b0-7d2a-7a49-6aae067fdcda"], "h6e69549bgb3d3g4dd9g8d21g4fab367d307d": ["She <i>murdered </i>my daughter.", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "c9694c23-59dd-9fa8-3f17-046875ba5cde"], "hffe25259g3fbdg4676g9facg6a821163b9c1": ["Killing Kagha won't bring her back. Don't do it. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "24f59877-4023-f354-a0df-954128b55260"], "h5a2f1465gfdc3g47d8ga813g6860b6166af0": ["Mari - look at her. She's miserable. Alone. <i>Pathetic. </i>", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "ccbc6174-5ac3-bcc3-8d6c-fedd90f5cd6b"], "h953ed078ga586g4208ga06fg08e52712849f": ["Don't let her drag you down with her. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "378f2f1f-baa9-8d68-64a9-55e90c1d07c0"], "h68595db1g1608g40dbg9c0cg516b353d08a3": ["Ngh!", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "e6a8ecfc-9c73-26a3-de9f-05bc34f955dd"], "h8e22d07bgf77bg49c2g8557gd21462c7dd3f": ["Let's go. Before I change my mind. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "9c654c2e-ac0d-7faa-32c2-b95487390931"], "h0af964f0g8317g43b4g9fd4g57757ef011b8": ["Death is too good for her. Let her suffer with what she's done. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "b231429e-62c3-bd3d-b2b5-3520f6cdb841"], "h1c6640e0g2808g4b00g8a18g00981f4cd382": ["Hm. You make a good point. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "98237c3e-0c4a-7ca5-0d4c-c9a0ec39450d"], "hc230b653gc7f6g4997g9561gefd95a6dc0bb": ["Remember this moment. Remember Arabella's cold, dead body. And live with the blood of an innocent child on your hands.", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "f39305cd-5632-3b37-e0e5-e9fd7f97d76d"], "hbe2f6051g63c4g4ae7g9552gf6ab93e201e0": ["Nnnngg...", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "14f6a0b3-593a-19a9-8f14-858e5489a717"], "h069c4a1bgdc98g45fag8110gb842cba72460": ["I didn't ask you. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "279bffc9-dc07-04f9-4f5f-3e7d056f5f7d"], "h94956b51gd7dag4855gad0cg9cdb04b3b6e6": ["Do you feel better now? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "20576073-3ef2-aa96-7e03-1b7edab3a390"], "h1cce19f2g5c6fg4383gaa93g79b2350d038b": ["It was never about feeling better. It was about justice.", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "d3a584d6-ea25-4afe-ffd9-f2a88b242c11"], "h79bdc3f0g5a7cg4753g81bfg1783690ff96d": ["Not like I was sleeping at night anyway. C'mon Locke. We're done. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "8e25e175-5862-a501-319b-7c489bb4de0f"], "h58f65a57g84c3g4781gb3b6g2c3770bdef59": ["That was a pointless waste of life. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "862dce5c-02fa-71fb-57f1-207802b401dd"], "h9b791be2g5002g425agaf8fg32167d81fc18": ["Then I guess Arabella and the snake now have something in common. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "c3f4e9aa-5045-e232-a281-d13cca3bd6ae"], "h9da34fdag8c9fg493ag9884ge8a801fa436e": ["C'mon Locke. We're done. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "7eff6b38-b108-f9b0-c048-e75b9d8096c6"], "h21c1e333ga042g44c2g905fga98955331f33": ["This will only cause more pain in the end.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "e37fae2b-2f6a-ce48-7289-a3555cacfde3"], "hcf474642gda65g4ad4g8b84g29468fe5c8b0": ["Slit her throat, or she'll summon help.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "8db2baaa-e9fd-b843-7633-33602cd42e23"], "hf287366bg7c8ag41d4g8218gb9e0bbc02459": ["As if I'd let her draw breath. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "318351a5-18c2-645b-40ea-89021119c13b"], "h809acbadg25d1g4af3gb2b9g3be26d50a34c": ["<i>Quietly watch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "6fed26e4-86a2-75b1-4cd7-814da0f9c73c"], "hf0f1c0abgc9f4g43f0g9debg99825504f76b": ["I'm sorry.... I'm... ", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "2059dc91-5780-f35c-e90f-70e2e1b61960"], "h9fd0818eg3742g428aga9b7g5d518d8a6abd": ["<i>Walk away. </i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "870e0fb4-de85-25bb-ed1e-9b85c10b60b3"], "h5925644bgd814g4638gaf90g25499b5b249c": ["Your daughter roused the nest. Did you expect the viper not to strike?", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "e95e283c-612e-6981-de6f-57f3bb3487b9"], "h8fdbb78eg8073g42f7gb5c8g657219cb73b4": ["I will bear no more accusations. Leave me.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\NPCs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "53879b2f-99d9-e404-e450-4efca8566b2e"]}